    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "Turn Thunderbird into a Neovim client.\n\nInstalling this addon requires the following additional steps:\n- Installing firenvim as a neovim plugin (see <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://github.com/glacambre/firenvim\">https://github.com/glacambre/firenvim</a>)\n- Running the `:call firenvim#install(0)` command.\n\n/!\\ To make Firenvim work in reply windows, you currently need to patch Thunderbird! See <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1675589\">https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1675589</a> for more information."
    },
